Rating: 4
THE BEST. I did it as written and then did it again with low fat dairy to see what would happen. Either way, it's wonderful. The only difference: I baked the kugel in 1/2 cup muffin tins; took less time and they look great on the table. 10 minutes before taking them out of the oven, I sprayed them with a bit of canola oil spray to make them look nicer.

